{"tid":1393483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 8.3遊行必需設立目標及撤退共識！否則會好似728咁慘敗！","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:02:13.000Z","uid":2617,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf95ef922118c2e09655f88768e469681f997f25","tid":1393483,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"8.3遊行已知道冇不反對通知書<br />\n所以大家如果要去行街<br />\n一係行完就走<br />\n如果要唔走就一定要搵目標<br />\n唔係既話就會好似728咁<br />\n好多手足比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n引用黑簡迪巴打呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1391030/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1391030/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n成功戰役共通點：<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n1. 有目標 並且能完成<br />\n612衝擊及阻止二讀<br />\n71衝入立法會<br />\n721突擊中聯辦<br />\n反觀損失較多既戰役<br />\n多數係未有目標/未有完成任何目標<br />\n致使前線留守<br />\n最終得不償失<br />\n<br />\n2. 有共識的時間線<br />\n其實同第一點都好類似<br />\n有共識完成一件事<br />\n就一齊撤退/轉移陣地<br />\n當沒有共識完成一件事<br />\n變成大家都沒有共識幾時退走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望大家一齊研究下星期六應該點做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0eeaa9144c280c5bef37c8f18d2985cb7235665d","tid":1393483,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"【突發】警方通知反對8.3＜旺角再遊行＞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nfor reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbd0a56a3285b06b4defe8f39b9602f02b71a96","tid":1393483,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"認同要有一個目標"},{"pid":"398763185e1a32ffd628944701e2e1673b5745ff","tid":1393483,"uid":163588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c